<node TEXT="commit cc29c85e599a67a0c13d844832ac7bb748685fb9&#xa;Author: David Collins &lt;collinsd@codeaurora.org&gt;&#xa;Date:   Fri Apr 29 16:30:22 2011 -0700&#xa;&#xa;    regulator: pm8921-regulator: modify pin-control interface + improvements&#xa;    &#xa;    Change pin control enabling from using regulator_set_mode to using&#xa;    regulator_enable.  This requires the use of a second semi-virtual&#xa;    regulator which is responsible for only pin control.  Consumers that&#xa;    wish to utilize pin control will need to call regulator_get for both&#xa;    the real and pin control regulator devices, along with other typical&#xa;    regulator framework functions.&#xa;    &#xa;    regulator_set_mode should now work the way expected by the regulator&#xa;    framework.  REGULATOR_MODE_NORMAL will correspond to HPM,&#xa;    REGULATOR_MODE_IDLE will correspond to LPM, and REGULATOR_MODE_FAST and&#xa;    REGULATOR_MODE_STANDBY will no longer be valid for the driver.&#xa;    &#xa;    Also, make improvements elsewhere in the pm8921-regulator driver.&#xa;    Change set_voltage callbacks so that the chosen set point is always&#xa;    between min_uV and max_uV instead of simply truncating min_uV.  If&#xa;    no set point exists between min_uV and max_uV, then the set_voltage&#xa;    callback should return an error.  Add list_voltage callbacks so that&#xa;    the regulator framework core can provide additional safety during&#xa;    regulator registration." ID="ID_1732548507" CREATED="1318535680196" MODIFIED="1318535680953">
<node TEXT="commit 170ab442f46682f45f5b0adfe732ed61323fb101&#xa;Author: David Collins &lt;collinsd@codeaurora.org&gt;&#xa;Date:   Mon May 2 11:39:09 2011 -0700&#xa;&#xa;    msm: board-msm8x60: add regulator names for saw regulators&#xa;    &#xa;    Fill in the regulator init_data constraint name so that it will&#xa;    be available to the saw-regulator driver.  This is a prerequisite&#xa;    to using dynamic data in the saw-regulator driver." ID="ID_1762158291" CREATED="1318535697405" MODIFIED="1318535698273">
