<node TEXT="commit 79cc0d370201a5d7de08e188505031d228bbe2a4&#xa;Author: Maheshkumar Sivasubramanian &lt;msivasub@codeaurora.org&gt;&#xa;Date:   Mon May 9 11:50:03 2011 -0600&#xa;&#xa;    msm: kconfig: config support for SPM version 1 and 2.&#xa;    &#xa;    Enable config support for the different versions of Subsystem Power&#xa;    Manager(SPM) in msm chipsets. SPM allows the CPU to enter low power&#xa;    modes when idle. MSM chipsets 7X30 and 8660 use version 1&#xa;    of the SPM hardware. Chipset 8960 supports version 2 of the SPM&#xa;    hardware." ID="ID_31418256" CREATED="1318539679167" MODIFIED="1318539679923"/>
