<node TEXT="commit 8360a729728d8f9e579f101c491e33eda8b7885a&#xa;Author: Abhijeet Dharmapurikar &lt;adharmap@codeaurora.org&gt;&#xa;Date:   Tue Jun 28 20:48:36 2011 -0700&#xa;&#xa;    power: pm8921-bms: read temperature and voltage via adc&#xa;    &#xa;    Read the battery temeperature and voltage from the adc driver instead&#xa;    of hard coding them in the driver.&#xa;    &#xa;    In the charing began and charing end functions, use&#xa;    pm8921_bms_get_percent_charge api. This prevents duplicating calling&#xa;    the adc functions." ID="ID_296667811" CREATED="1318543966077" MODIFIED="1318543966850">
